With NBA news coming at a slow pace, the league's social media mavens have honed their hashtag game skills. After the successes of #NBAmusicians and #NBASitcoms, it was time for a new one Wednesday. And with Marvel's "Guardians of the Galaxy" opening in theaters Thursday night, the stage was set perfectly for #NBASuperheroes. Teams broke out their puns and their Photoshop skills and created some gems.